display.description: A profile template in the same style as standard flow profiles on Decent machines.  Standard flow profiles consist of 3 stages: preinfusion, hold, and decline.  This template includes all of the same variables in each stage that are controllable via sliders in the similar Decent profiles.   This base standard profile type is used to create many other profiles on Decent machines such as 'Flow Profile for Milky Drinks'and others.  The same can be done with this profile on the Meticulous by duplicating this template, setting the variable values, and saving it as a different name.
